  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <section class="intro-section">
  <h2>Expert Life Care Planning for Nicholasville Catastrophic Injury Cases</h2>
  <p class="lead">When catastrophic injuries require comprehensive future care planning, Nicholasville attorneys trust Skerritt Economics for CLCP-certified life care plans that accurately project lifetime medical costs and care needs. Our detailed assessments provide the foundation for securing appropriate compensation for your clients' future medical requirements.</p>

  <p>Our life care plans are developed with knowledge of Nicholasville Ky's healthcare infrastructure, including local hospitals, rehabilitation facilities, home health agencies, and specialized medical providers. This ensures accurate cost projections and practical care recommendations.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <section class="services-section">
  <h2>Life Care Planning Services in Nicholasville</h2>
  <div class="services-grid">
  <div class="service-card">
  <i class="icon icon-life-care icon-xl"></i>
  <h3>Comprehensive Life Care Plans</h3>
  <p>Detailed assessment of all future medical needs including surgeries, therapies, medications, and equipment for Nicholasville area catastrophic injury victims.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
  <i class="icon icon-chart icon-xl"></i>
  <h3>Future Medical Cost Projections</h3>
  <p>Accurate cost estimates based on Nicholasville area healthcare pricing, inflation factors, and lifetime care requirements with present value calculations.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
  <i class="icon icon-medical icon-xl"></i>
  <h3>Assistive Technology & Equipment</h3>
  <p>Assessment of durable medical equipment, assistive technology, home modifications, and vehicle adaptations needed for maximum independence.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
  <i class="icon icon-care icon-xl"></i>
  <h3>Care Coordination Planning</h3>
  <p>Evaluation of nursing care, attendant care, case management, and therapeutic interventions required throughout the client's lifetime.</p>
  </div>
  </div>
  </section>

