  <!-- Methodology -->
  <section class="methodology-section">
  <h2>Life Care Planning Methodology</h2>
  <p>Our CLCP-certified approach ensures comprehensive and life care plans that meet Kentucky court standards:</p>
  <ul class="methodology-list">
  <li><strong>Medical Record Review:</strong> Thorough analysis of all medical documentation and prognosis</li>
  <li><strong>Physician Collaboration:</strong> Consultation with treating physicians and medical specialists</li>
  <li><strong>Needs Assessment:</strong> Identification of all future medical, therapeutic, and equipment needs</li>
  <li><strong>Cost Research:</strong> Current Nicholasville area pricing for all recommended services and items</li>
  <li><strong>Present Value Analysis:</strong> Economic calculations for lifetime cost projections</li>
  </ul>
  </section>

